  <body>

    <div class="container">
    
      <div class="row-fluid heading">
        <div class="span12">
          <h1><img src="./img/launcher.png" alt="Herbalist icon"> Herbalist</h1>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row-fluid subheading">
        <div class="span12">
          <p class="lead">Healing herb lexicon in your pocket.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row-fluid pitch">

        <div class="span5 offset1 video">
          <img src="./img/herbalist.png" alt="Herbalist app">
        </div>
        
        <div class="span5 actions">
          <div class="span8 offset2">
            <div class="statistics">
              <div class="span4">
                <div class="linediv-l">
                  <h3><%= count %></h3> <p>backers</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="span4">
                <div class="linediv-c">
                  <h3><%= Math.round(money * 100) / 100 %></h3> <p>of 10 BTC</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="span4">
                <div class="linediv-r">
                  <h3><%= days %></h3> <p>days left</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="span10 offset1">
            <div class="thermometer progress active">
              <div class="bar bar-success" style="width: <%= Math.min(money*10, 100) %>%;"></div>
              <div class="bar bar-warning" style="width: <%= 100 - Math.min(money*10, 100) %>%;"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="span6 offset3 order">
            <a class="coinbase-button" data-code="f53f62fe7290eb7f65b9b4cf278cfd1f" href="https://coinbase.com/checkouts/f53f62fe7290eb7f65b9b4cf278cfd1f">Support with Bitcoin</a><script src="https://coinbase.com/assets/button.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
          </div>

          <div class="span8 offset2 social">
            <!-- AddThis Button BEGIN -->
	    <div class="addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style addthis_32x32_style">
	      <a class="addthis_button_facebook"></a>
	      <a class="addthis_button_twitter"></a>
	      <a class="addthis_button_compact"></a><a class="addthis_counter addthis_bubble_style"></a>
	    </div>
	    <script type="text/javascript">var addthis_config = {"data_track_addressbar":true};</script>
	    <script type="text/javascript" src="//s7.addthis.com/js/300/addthis_widget.js#pubid=ra-51faa7d83bcb7502"></script>
	    <!-- AddThis Button END -->
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row-fluid section1">
        <div class="span5 offset1 asset">
          <img src="./img/section1.jpg" >
        </div>
        <div class="span5 copy">
          <p>
<b>Welcome to Herbalist crowdfunding site.</b>
<br><br>Love picking the healing herbs?
<br><br>You will also love <b>Herbalist</b>, a complete lexicon of common healing herbs for Android.
Herbalist helps you identify the plants by name, category, appearance or disease they can heal. 
You can also notice all hidden places where your favorite herbs grow.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row-fluid section2">
        <div class="span5 offset1 copy copy-right">
          <p>
There is still lot of work on Herbalist.
Right now we need experienced botanists and illustrators to create a really outstanding herb database.
<br><br>Click <b>Pay with Bitcoin</b> to help us collect enough resources for further development.
Every supporter will get a free license when Herbalist is ready.
<br><br>Also spread the word about Herbalist on Twitter, Facebook or your favorite network. Thank you!
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="span5 asset">
          <img class="img-polaroid" src="./img/section2.jpg" >
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="row-fluid faq">
        <div class="span10 offset1">
          <h3>FAQ</h3>
          <div class="accordion" id="accordion2">

            <div class="accordion-group">
              <div class="accordion-heading">
                <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapseOne">
                  What is the current status of Herbalist?
                </a>
              </div>
              <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-body collapse">
                <div class="accordion-inner">
                  So far, the basic Android client is work in progress.
                  Currently, the database update from our Herbalist server is being implemented.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="accordion-group">
              <div class="accordion-heading">
                <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapseTwo">
                  What are the killer features?
                </a>
              </div>
              <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-body collapse">
                <div class="accordion-inner">
                  The app can filter the herb database by various keys like flower color or leaf shape.
                  It can also navigate to previously stored places where certain herbs grow.
                  The database is stored for offline usage as there may be some connection problems in terrain.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-group">
              <div class="accordion-heading">
                <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapseThree">
                  When Herbalist will be ready?
                </a>
              </div>
              <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-body collapse">
                <div class="accordion-inner">
                  It depends on your support. The app self should be available later this year.
                  The database will be filled step by step, based on available resources.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-group">
              <div class="accordion-heading">
                <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapseFour">
                  Why should I use Bitcoins?
                </a>
              </div>
              <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-body collapse">
                <div class="accordion-inner">
                  <a href="https://www.weusecoins.com/">Bitcoins</a> is a virtual currency that is fast and secure to transfer. 
                  If the crowdfunding goal <b>10 BTC</b> (cca 800 EUR) won't be reached by <b>October 31, 2013</b>, 
                  the money will be returned to the backers.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>


          </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="row-fluid footer">
        <div class="span12">
          <p>Created by <a href="http://carabana.cz">76house</a>.</p>
        </div>
